# Audio assets (per BIBLE v3 §6 — offline-first, Capacitor-bundled)
# Ignore WAV/AIFF anywhere в audio/ (твърде големи за git), но **позволи** JSON
# manifest файлове (нужни за UI development без local audio).
audio/**/*.wav
audio/**/*.aiff
audio/**/*.mp3
audio/**/*.m4a
audio/raw/
audio_files/
audio_files_safe39/
audio_files_safe39_normalized/
audio_files_list.txt
normalize_report_*.csv
# Beta: локално в audio/presets/, обслужвани от ngrok/local dev server.
# Production: copied to android/app/src/main/assets/audio/ от build script.
# Distribution: GitHub Releases (не Git LFS).
# audio_files/ = Тихол's raw .wav source library (local only)

